nal pending-to-success proof, and crash/recovery controls.\n\n## Current status\n\nProspective implementation only. Live repository-governance evidence is absent, G0-G5 acceptance is unestablished, and independent review remains blocked. This PR is intentionally draft until exact-head attempt-one push and pull-request CI pass and the formal read-only preflight is green.\n\n## Local verification\n\n- exact staged and committed tree: 1,183 tests passed;\n- Ruff and compile passed;\n- CI-delta, workflow registry, mission loop, claim registry, seal registry, and supply-chain guards passed;\n- no provider, model, scientific workflow, or external spend used.","created_at":"2026-07-19T19:02:47Z","updated_at":"2026-07-19T19:48:20Z","closed_at":"2026-07-19T19:48:20Z","merged_at":"2026-07-19T19:48:19Z","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/pulls/87/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/pulls/87/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/issues/87/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/manfromnowhere143/telos/statuses/56fb78f5f8afcd8709fde1170e8422072626f367","head":{"label":"manfromnowhere143:agent/iter239-repository-governance","ref":"agent/iter239-repository-governance","sha":"56fb78f5f8afcd8709fde1170e8422072626f367","user":{"login":"manfromnowhere143","id":193130714,"node_id":"U_kgDOC4Lw2g","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/193130714?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/manfromnowhere143","html_url":"https://github.com/manfromnowhere143","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/manfromnowhere143/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/manfromnowhere143/following{/other_user}","gists_